|        |       |         |
|        +-------+         |
|                          |
+--------------------------+
The box is roughly 6% of the frame radius.

What inside_box() does
def inside_box(pt, box):
    x, y = pt
    l, t, r, b = box
    return (l <= x <= r) and (t <= y <= b)
It checks:

