If the face leaves the stable box (inside == False) → start SEEKING

SEEKING: “move gimbal to recenter”

If face gets close enough to center (within_stop_thresh == True) → go back to LOCKED

This is hysteresis-like behavior:

one condition to start moving (box boundary)

a different condition to stop moving (radial threshold)
This reduces oscillation/jitter at the edge.

